OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTwitter confirms users' fee
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto buy verification        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Twitter has confirmed plans to allow   
OL,6, users to buy blue-tick verified status.
OL,8,FIn an update for Apple devices, the    
OL,9,Fcompany said the feature would be open 
OL,10,Fto users in certain countries who sign 
OL,11,Fup to its Twitter Blue service for     
OL,12,F$7.99 (#7) per month.                  
OL,14,FThe policy change is controversial,    
OL,15,Famid concerns that the platform could  
OL,16,Fbe swamped with fake accounts.         
OL,18,FIt follows Twitter's takeover by Elon  
OL,19,FMusk, who on Friday laid off around    
OL,20,Fhalf of the company's workforce.       
